Just after hitting merge the message "Unable to merge An unexpected error occurred" is displayed.

The error code returned is:

{code}
#!python

00be0a4999e744739d4f7d856a88c05b$829a7adaac6e31f598a8e1aab195a2a5
{code}

This may be the same as [Issue BCLOUD-6847|https://bitbucket.org/site/master/issue/6847/keep-seeing-merge-failed-error-when] that seems halted.

{{#commit-filter}} has a {{z-index}} of 2, which makes it appear over the user dropdown menu.\\
This can be fixed by setting {{#user-dropdown}}&#x27;s {{z-index}} to 3:

{code}
#!css

#user-dropdown {
    z-index: 3;
}
{code}
